	* ftp-ls.c: Replaced indent tabs by spaces.
	* ftp.c: Likewise.
	* utils.c: Removed read_whole_file() definition.
	* netrc.c: Removed read_whole_file() definition for STANDALONE.
	* utils.h: Removed read_whole_file() declaration.

