	adjust_extension.
	* http.c (gethttp): Ditto.
	* convert.c (local_quote_string): Ditto.

	* init.c (commands): Add "adjustextension", and reflect rename
	change for opt.adjust_extension, for both "adjustextension" and
	"htmlextension".

