	* host.c (lookup_host): Use sizeof(ip4_address) to calculate the
	offset.
	(address_list_new): Use map_ipv4_to_ip.
	(wget_sockaddr_set_address): Convert ADDR to IPv4 before using it
	in IPv4 context.

