2001-04-08  Jan Prikryl  <prikryl@cg.tuwien.ac.at>

	* ftp-ls.c (ftp_parse_winnt_ls): The AM/PM change did assume
	12:01PM == 00:01, which was obviously wrong. Taken care of this
	anomaly.

