	* ftp.c (ftp_loop_internal): Disable padding.
	(getftp): Ditto.

	* http.c (http_loop): Disable padding.

	* retr.c (show_progress): Use it to enable padding.

	* retr.c (rate): Optional parameter PAD for padding the rate.

