	(retrieve_url): Allow heuristic adding of html.

	* url.c (url_filename): Don't use the `%' in Windows file names.

	* http.c (http_loop): Always time-stamp the local file.

	* http.c (http_loop): Ditto.

	* ftp.c (ftp_retrieve_list): Use it.

